	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What I need to know is if the mroms used on these boards uses the same nintendo pinout mentioned on the wiki?  I saw no mention about it.
<br />
<br />The board already is different than nintendo's ones since the side with the chips is on the front of the cart: nintendo ones are on the back.
<br />
<br />Anybody have any information about this?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
