	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was able today to check the pinout for the Lagrange Point Mask rom. The result is that it's <strong>not the same</strong> as the nintendo one. I used Kevin Horton document as a reference for the VRC-VII pins.
<br />
<br />Here's my current draft of the pins:
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">PRG ROM - 512KBytes &#40;32pin&#41;:&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Lagrange point &#40;VRCVII&#41;- 512KBytes &#40;32pin&#41; :<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ---_---&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ---_---<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A17 - |01&nbsp; &nbsp;32| - +5V&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;+5V&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- |01&nbsp; &nbsp;32| - +5V<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A18 - |02&nbsp; &nbsp;31| - +5V&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&#40;VRC-VII-23&#41; PRG A16 - |02&nbsp; &nbsp;31| - A18&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&#40;VRC-VII-26&#41;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A15 - |03&nbsp; &nbsp;30| - +5V&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&#40;VRC-VII-22&#41; PRG A15 - |03&nbsp; &nbsp;30| - A17&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&#40;VRC-VII-25&#41;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A12 - |04&nbsp; &nbsp;29| - PRG A14&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A12 - |04&nbsp; &nbsp;29| - PRG A14 &#40;VRC-VII-21&#41;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A7&nbsp; - |05&nbsp; &nbsp;28| - PRG A13&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; PRG A7&nbsp; - |05&nbsp; &nbsp;28| - PRG A13 &#40;VRC-VII-20&#41;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A6&nbsp; - |06&nbsp; &nbsp;27| - PRG A8 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; PRG A6&nbsp; - |06&nbsp; &nbsp;27| - PRG A8<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A5&nbsp; - |07&nbsp; &nbsp;26| - PRG A9&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A5&nbsp; - |07&nbsp; &nbsp;26| - PRG A9<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A4&nbsp; - |08&nbsp; &nbsp;25| - PRG A11 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A4&nbsp; - |08&nbsp; &nbsp;25| - PRG A11<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A3&nbsp; - |09&nbsp; &nbsp;24| - PRG A16&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; PRG A3&nbsp; - |09&nbsp; &nbsp;24| - PRG /CE &#40;VRC-VII-44&#41;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A2&nbsp; - |10&nbsp; &nbsp;23| - PRG A10&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; PRG A2&nbsp; - |10&nbsp; &nbsp;23| - PRG A10 <br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A1&nbsp; - |11&nbsp; &nbsp;22| - PRG /CE&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; PRG A1&nbsp; - |11&nbsp; &nbsp;22| - GND<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A0&nbsp; - |12&nbsp; &nbsp;21| - PRG D7&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG A0&nbsp; - |12&nbsp; &nbsp;21| - PRG D7<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG D0&nbsp; - |13&nbsp; &nbsp;20| - PRG D6&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; PRG D0&nbsp; - |13&nbsp; &nbsp;20| - PRG D6&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG D1&nbsp; - |14&nbsp; &nbsp;19| - PRG D5&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG D1&nbsp; - |14&nbsp; &nbsp;19| - PRG D5<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG D2&nbsp; - |15&nbsp; &nbsp;18| - PRG D4&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PRG D2&nbsp; - |15&nbsp; &nbsp;18| - PRG D4<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;GND&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- |16&nbsp; &nbsp;17| - PRG D3&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;GND&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- |16&nbsp; &nbsp;17| - PRG D3<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -------&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -------<br /></div>
<br />
<br />I will try to check the VRC-VI mask roms once I have a chance.
<br />
<br />Should we put this content on the wiki? I guess it can be inserted in the pinout section.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
